item.title: 667/711 how can i make myself and owner?
item.dc:creator: @Its_ema Its ema
item.description:
@Its_ema wrote:

  1. Go into commands.java search for “troy” or “optimus” if your using optimusscape. Replace all that with your name.

  2. Into player.java, search for =2, rename the playername into yours.

  3. to give someone amdin or owner, copy the same code in player.java, but change the name to that players name.

1 for mod, 2 for admin.
